  "ftbquests.chapter.252FC81556BE3D4B.quest7990469202542007160.description1": "击败\u00266{entity.fdbosses.malkuth}\u0026r掉落",
  "ftbquests.chapter.252FC81556BE3D4B.quest7990469202542007160.subtitle": "\u00266{entity.fdbosses.malkuth}\u0026r的核心",
  "ftbquests.chapter.252FC81556BE3D4B.quest8872242641152191514.description1": "使用\u00266{item.minecraft.brush}\u0026r在\u00266{advancements.cataclysm.cursed_pyramid.title}\u0026r中刷扫\u00266{block.minecraft.suspicious_sand}\u0026r概率获得",
  "ftbquests.chapter.252FC81556BE3D4B.quest8872242641152191514.subtitle": "\u00266{entity.cataclysm.ancient_remnant}\u0026r的随葬品",
  "ftbquests.chapter.252FC81556BE3D4B.title": "重要物品",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.description1": "\u00266Discord: \u0026dhttps://discord.gg/CVsAWVay&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.description10": "\u0026b主城：El_mal（玩建造的牢E）&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.description11": "\u0026b地形：wonderful艾辰&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.description12": "\u0026b定制动画：merlin204&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.description13": "\u0026b定制美术：Ao， 一只路过的小吴，XVIII-ling\u0026r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.description14": "\u0026b以及：诸位优秀的模组、资源包及光影包作者&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.description15": "——P1nero",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.description2": "\u00266QQ交流1群: \u0026d948180812&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.description3": "感谢一路走来的小伙伴们！感谢各位优秀的模组作者！这是我第二次制作整合包，如果你对模拟经营感兴趣，可以尝试我的另一款整合包：",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.description4": "\u0026a《SkilletMan》\u0026r！",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.description5": "远梦之棺这个名最初是我朋友想的，当时我们打算制作一款载入史册的模组，但由于一些原因我们没有走到最后...",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.description6": "\u00266《远梦之棺》，意为将美好的东西存封在精致的小盒子里沉睡，正如我们所降临的废墟一般。\u0026r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.description7": "玩过\u0026a《SkilletMan》\u0026r的朋友应该都知道，我个人并不喜欢将任务剧情以及所有交互都堆积在FTB界面里完成，因此在本整合包中，FTB任务将更多地扮演图鉴的作用，并随着世界里的交互逐渐解锁，我们的剧情展开和物品收集主要还是通过NPC对话来展现。",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.description8": "我也不喜欢盲目堆砌模组，本整合包主线采用的敌对Boss模组都是较适合使用史诗战斗来交互的。本整合包采用最新的史诗战斗12，带你体验全新的史诗战斗附属，证明史诗战斗强大的潜力所在。",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.description9": "\u0026b鸣谢：&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.subtitle": "“传说深海之中有一片废墟，守望着这个世界”",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.task.325688042160411882.title": "本整合包处于测试阶段，主城仍未完善，部分区域未解锁（真的没有藏宝箱！）",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.task.3257333974082388709.title": "如果没有出现其他章节的话，去附近逛逛吧～",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.task.8806221034708452812.title": "\u00266本整合包并不会向你收取任何费用！仅在CurseForge平台发布，严禁第三方分发，任何第三方转载（包括使用网盘）均为侵权行为！欢迎举报！\u0026r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.quest711034741643803066.title": "作者的话",
  "ftbquests.chapter.16AFC8ED236C979B.title": "序章",
  "ftbquests.chapter.522B859BEE1EDD88.quest348391678466111360.description1": "将\u0026b{item.armourers_workshop.skin-template}\u0026r放入\u0026d{block.armourers_workshop.skin-library}\u0026r，可以取出我们喜欢的时装。",
  "ftbquests.chapter.522B859BEE1EDD88.quest348391678466111360.description2": "之后，可以使用\u00266{block.armourers_workshop.skinning-table}\u0026r，或默认按下\u00266[ctrl + p]\u0026r{keys.armourers_workshop.open-wardrobe}，装饰自己。",
  "ftbquests.chapter.522B859BEE1EDD88.quest5237705525294358869.description1": "右键\u0026d{block.armourers_workshop.skin-library-global}\u0026r可以从中挑选自己喜欢的时装并下载时装文件到\u0026a本地\u0026r。",
  "ftbquests.chapter.522B859BEE1EDD88.quest7469604769731266141.description1": "使用\u00266{block.armourers_workshop.skinning-table}\u0026r可以将时装和物品绑定在一起，使我们可以在不同的武器下使用不同的时装",
  "ftbquests.chapter.522B859BEE1EDD88.quest9076002229603668648.rich_description1": "使用&6{block.armourers_workshop.skinning-table}&r，可以将",
  "ftbquests.chapter.522B859BEE1EDD88.quest9076002229603668648.rich_description2": "§6{block.armourers_workshop.skin-library-global}§f",
  "ftbquests.chapter.522B859BEE1EDD88.quest9076002229603668648.rich_description3": "里的时装取出来",
  "ftbquests.chapter.522B859BEE1EDD88.title": "\u0026a化形秘术",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest1470580929012265040.description1": "\u0026b{epicfight.skill_slot.sword_soaring}\u0026r乃本整合包的主要跑图方式",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest1470580929012265040.description2": "习得\u0026b{skill.epicfight.sword_soaring.category}\u0026r即可释放飞行技能，自由御剑飞行。",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest1470580929012265040.description3": "默认按\u00266[K]\u0026r查看技能",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest1470580929012265040.subtitle": "炁引八荒，劍禦六合",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest1470580929012265040.task.4276696466893631127.title": "{key.sword_soaring.common}",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest1470580929012265040.title": "{epicfight.skill_slot.sword_soaring}",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest1892043973836821613.description1": "本整合包矿物来源主要来自击败魔物",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest1892043973836821613.description2": "\u0026d{entity.minecraft.pillager}：概率掉落{item.minecraft.gold_ingot}、{item.minecraft.diamond}、{item.minecraft.netherite_ingot}\u0026r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest1892043973836821613.description3": "\u0026b所有敌对生物：概率掉落{item.minecraft.iron_ingot}、{item.minecraft.amethyst_shard}、{item.fantasy_armor.moon_crystal}\u0026r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest1892043973836821613.task.719282771427451075.title": "冒险包何须挖矿",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest1892043973836821613.title": "矿物说明",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest3288439856153403711.description1": "\u0026d{entity.monsterexpansion.skrythe}\u0026r是栖息在高海拔地区\u0026a（风袭沙砾丘陵 / 沙砾山地）\u0026r的魔物，可使用\u00266{item.minecraft.nether_star}\u0026r驯服",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest3288439856153403711.image0": "{image:tcrcore:textures/ftb/blue_dragon.png width:160 height:90 align:center}",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest3288439856153403711.subtitle": "驯服\u0026d{entity.monsterexpansion.skrythe}\u0026r，骑着它翱翔天际！",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest3288439856153403711.title": "驯龙高手",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest3443231341170901454.title": "{block.tudigong.tudi_temple}",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest3443231341170901454.description1": "在\u0026a大部分村庄\u0026r之中你将找到\u00266{block.tudigong.tudi_temple}\u0026r，它可以为你指引方向。",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest3443231341170901454.description2": "古籍有云：",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest3443231341170901454.description3": "\u00266{block.tudigong.tudi_temple}\u0026r和\u0026d{item.tudigong.tudi_command_spell}\u0026r皆可合成",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest3443231341170901454.description4": "在\u00266{block.tudigong.tudi_temple}\u0026r边上\u00263潜行三次\u0026r即可召唤{entity.tudigong.tudigong}",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest3443231341170901454.description5": "在\u00266{block.tudigong.tudi_temple}\u0026r边上\u00263插上{block.minecraft.torch}\u0026r即可祈福",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest5366344467862019140.description1": "\u0026b{itemGroup.ParCool}\u0026r是一项很酷的运动，让我们可以轻松爬上三格高的地方，翻越障碍等，移动更加地灵活。",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest5366344467862019140.description2": "在本整合包中你将体会到\u0026b{itemGroup.ParCool}\u0026r与\u00266{key.epicfight.system}\u0026r兼容的魅力！",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest5366344467862019140.description3": "\u0026b常用的{itemGroup.ParCool}手法有：\u0026r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest5366344467862019140.description4": "起跳时按住\u00266[右键]\u0026r以{key.parcool.ClingToCliff}",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest5366344467862019140.description5": "即将落地时按\u00266[R]\u0026r键以{key.parcool.Breakfall}",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest5366344467862019140.description6": "更多精彩可在{parcool.patchouli.guide.name}中学习，\u0026c本整合包禁用了部分{itemGroup.ParCool}按键以免冲突\u0026r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest5366344467862019140.task.4463507524228208334.title": "{itemGroup.ParCool}",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest7487272814909384521.description1": "本整合包安装了\u0026b{key.fast_tpa.category}\u0026r模组，丰富多人游玩体验！",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest7487272814909384521.description2": "默认按下\u00266[右ALT]\u0026r即可{key.fast_tpa.send}！",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest7487272814909384521.description3": "可自定义救难信号文本，以及前去支援时的文本",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest7487272814909384521.subtitle": "“{key.fast_tpa.category}”",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest7487272814909384521.task.5950346987720516679.title": "{key.fast_tpa.category}",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest8224116903557449688.description1": "\u0026a{entity.ribbits.ribbit}\u0026r是一种很可爱的生物，但是除了可爱以外它并没有什么用。",
  "ftbquests.chapter.5A7C68B10CEA5C38.quest8224116903557449688.description2": "当然，世界上除了{entity.ribbits.ribbit}，还有许多\u0026e奇珍异兽\u0026r，它们的掉落物可以制作成各种各样的\u0026d法宝\u0026r！",
